 American pop star. While Rihanna is known to be “unapologetic,” posing nude and topless at random, our own Tiwa Savage is following in her footsteps. Rihanna shuns Super Bowl(Opens in a new browser tab) Known in the past for her decent stage appearance and less exposure of her skin, Tiwa Savage has of recent continued on the negative path of revealing her treasured body. Her latest raunchy photos are causing a buzz on social media. In the photos, the diva strips down to show off her new under-hip tattoo, causing tongues to wag that the mother of one has thrown caution to the wind. Vanguard. Fans of Nigerian pop diva, Tiwa Savage have urged her to leave nudity in music videos for the younger generations. May 23, 2017 In "Entertainment" Ending years of speculated feud and battle for supremacy, afro-beat songstress Tiwa Savage sent out her best regards to Yemi Alade popularly known as Mama Africa over the release of her album, Woman of Steel. September 7, 2019 In "Entertainment" Nigerian multi-award winning hip-hop singer, songwriter and Hypertek Records boss, Innocent '2face' Idibia, has cautioned Nigerians against making distasteful jokes from the marriage crisis of Mavin's first-lady, Tiwa Savage and her husband Tunji ‘Teebillz’ Balogun. May 1, 2016 In "Entertainment"